OL,6,FThe RAIB recommended that Southern
OL,7,FRailways' parent company Govia
OL,8,FThameslink Railway (GTR) improves its
OL,9,Ffatigue management process.
OL,11,FGTR's safety, health and security
OL,12,Fdirector Samantha Facey said: "Safety
OL,13,Fis always our number one priority and
OL,14,Fwe're determined to learn from every
OL,15,Fincident to improve our safety
OL,16,Fstandard for our people and our
OL,17,Fcustomers.
OL,19,F"We're committed to making sure our
OL,20,Fstaff are fit and alert when they're
OL,21,Fat work.
