OL,6,F"In August, we updated and improved
OL,7,Four fatigue risk management standard
OL,8,Fto help us manage fatigue more
OL,9,Feffectively, which includes reports
OL,10,Ffrom staff related to tiredness.
OL,12,F"We've also set up stronger working
OL,13,Fgroups with staff representatives, and
OL,14,Fwe're now using robust scientific
OL,15,Fmodelling to plan staff shifts so we
OL,16,Fcan spot and prevent fatigue before it
OL,17,Fbecomes a risk.
